snippet.title: Grounded: Fully Yoked Edition Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The ultimate Grounded experience is now bulging with content that's sure to get you pumped! Fully Yoked Edition contains all previously released content updates along with new ant queens, new game + mode, and an array of exciting new gear. Are you ready to get Fully Yoked? Grounded: Fully Yoked Edition is available April 16, 2024.

https://www.xbox.com/games/grounded
